data.description: Our team is delighted to present this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom property in the charming Winter Garden neighborhood. From the moment you step inside, you'll be amazed by the flawless white porcelain tiles that grace the entire first floor, giving the home a chic and contemporary atmosphere. The open layout is perfect for hosting family and friends, creating memories that will last a lifetime. The half bathroom has been completely renovated, boasting large floor-to-ceiling mirrors and gorgeous black stone accents against the white floors. All the bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, while the second floor offers an extra spacious family room. This is the perfect home for a family seeking a friendly and gated community. Lake View Preserve is known for its vibrant community spirit and numerous resident activities, providing ample opportunities to meet new and wonderful people. Don't hesitate to schedule a viewing, as this home won't stay on the market for long.
